# Continual Test-time adaptation on SHIFT dataset
## environment setup
```
conda env create -f environment.yml
pip install -v -e . 
conda activate SHIFT_Seg
```
## Run
```
bash run_base.sh
bash run_tent.sh
bash run_cotta.sh
# Example rerun logs are included in ./example_logs/base.log, tent.log, and cotta.log.
```

